A very simple bash script to format /sys/devices/platform/smapi/BATX infomation, then output like this:

==========VENDOR INFORMATION==========
model:          42T4661
barcoding:              1ZH4708K0JX
serial:         717
manufacturer:           SANYO
manufacture_date:               2010-08-19

==========PRODUCT INFORMATION==========
design_capacity:        66240 mWh
design_voltage:         14.40 V
cycle_count:            33

==========STATUS INFORMATION===========
temperature:            27.00 C
remaining_percent:      45 %
